Class ExtendedExpression<T extends ExtendedExpression<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.peierls.expr.Expression

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TrigonometricExpression

    public abstract class ExtendedExpression<T extends ExtendedExpression<T>>
extends Expression
    Abstract base for expression subtypes that wrap existing expressions to provide new methods.
